[SN]TITLE[SN]
300 to attend Cardiff Traverse Blogging Conference

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
About 300 bloggers were expected to attend one of the UK's biggest travel blogging conferences in Cardiff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Speakers included Abigail King, who swapped a career as a doctor to be a blogger, photographer Rich McCor and The Travel Hack author Monica Stott.
There were digital skills workshops and a tour of the city on offer.
Deputy tourism minister Ken Skates said the Traverse Blogging Conference would "create a buzz about Cardiff and Wales" on social media.
